h1. grailsUiExtensions

This bean provides the implementations of the [displayMessage|uiExtensionMethods] and [displayFlashMessage|uiExtensionMethods] methods, and access to the values set for the tags to render messages, as well as access to plugin-namespaced Session. Flash and Request attributes

See the [UiExtensions|api:org.grails.plugin.platform.ui.UiExtensions] javadocs for details.

